title: What number of written complaints have been received and in relation to what services?
analysis_commentary: The picture presented for 2012/13 was that in comparable organisations, complaints for Hospital and Community Health Services (HCHS) had increased slightly, compared to 2011/12 (by 1.9%).
data_source: Health & Social Care Information Centre, Data on written complaints
